lyrics:
[Verse]
Elisa's feeling dizzy, spinning round and round
Her head is in a whirlwind, dizzy feelings confound
But we'll dance through the chaos, together by her side
Sending love and healing vibes, in this wild dance ride

[Chorus]
Elisa, get better quick, we're supporting you
We'll dance our way to healing, with every move we groove
The beat will lift your spirits, make those dizziness fade away
Elisa, we're here for you, dancing through the pain
